having an intimate family by their side.

574
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:12,240
I beg you that for the sake of the children,

575
00:36:13,500 --> 00:36:16,760
forgive me this one time.

576
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:19,240
Let me stay in this house!

577
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:20,440
Darling Second...

578
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:24,440
It's exactly because of the children

579
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,200
and because of you

580
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,880
that I sought the House of Yu for marriage.

581
00:36:28,680 --> 00:36:31,600
But they repeatedly refused it.

582
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,560
What was the reason?

583
00:36:38,980 --> 00:36:41,960
Their family...

584
00:36:41,960 --> 00:36:43,680
disliked my lowly background.

585
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:46,120
They wouldn't allow their legitimate daughter

586
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:49,120
to attend to you together with me.

587
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:52,400
The House of Yu is already like that.

588
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:55,360
How much more the other noble families,

589
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:56,160
Darling Second?

590
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,560
You're still lying to me!

591
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,880
I repeatedly gave you a chance.

592
00:37:05,200 --> 00:37:09,560
In my heart, I still think you to be kind.

593
00:37:12,430 --> 00:37:14,800
But did you tell me any truths?

594
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:18,080
Even one truth!

595
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:21,480
Darling Second...

596
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,560
Darling Second...

597
00:37:36,200 --> 00:37:37,200
Manniang,

598
00:37:39,450 --> 00:37:41,080
you said that you were left with no choice.

599
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:43,520
That you can only die.

600
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:47,440
So delicate.

601
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,480
So bashful.

602
00:37:50,120 --> 00:37:51,400
You cause people to pity you.

603
00:37:53,760 --> 00:37:55,120
I then settled you down.

604
00:37:57,880 --> 00:38:01,560
For you, I exerted all efforts.

605
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:07,000
I had children with you.

606
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:10,600
For you,

607
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:12,760
I sought marriage with the House of Yu.

608
00:38:15,160 --> 00:38:15,920
But you...

609
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:20,478
First, you caused Old Madam Yu

610
00:38:20,478 --> 00:38:21,480
to faint from anger.

611
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:26,520
Next, you fooled Xiaocui

612
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,364
so she brought the children to

613
00:38:28,364 --> 00:38:29,200
destroy my marriage plan.

614
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:32,120
Why did you do

615
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,840
all these things?

616
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:35,880
Don't you just want to

617
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,840
become the main wife of my Marquis Manor?

618
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,560
but now

619
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:48,240
I'm now penniless.

620
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,480
You then thought of taking away all my wealth

621
00:38:53,570 --> 00:38:54,228
and look for another rich man

622
00:38:54,228 --> 00:38:54,760
to make connections with.

623
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:56,960
I've seen through

624
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:58,920
so many schemes and intrigues.

625
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:00,760
I never suspected you!

626
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:02,440
Never once!

627
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,440
What's the use of killing you?

628
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,960
I'm the one who's stupid.

629
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:18,240
I got harmed by you.

630
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:21,120
I got fooled by you.

631
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:24,280
You were able to suck the blood from my neck.

632
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,440
You carried and played with me

633
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,360
like some wooden puppet!

634
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:30,280
I'm the one who's a dumb.

635
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,360
I admit it.

636
00:39:36,160 --> 00:39:37,240
But if you...

637
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:42,320
if you don't pack your things now and leave

638
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,360
the capital by tomorrow,

639
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:45,320
I'll make it unbearable for you

640
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,400
to live here in the capital!

641
00:39:49,080 --> 00:39:49,640
Darling Second!

642
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:50,720
Were you able

643
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:52,920
to hear clearly

644
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:56,440
every word I said?

645
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:07,880
Darling Second...

646
00:41:06,110 --> 00:41:06,840
What about there?

647
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:07,640
Nothing.

648
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:09,440
Also nothing!

649
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:10,480
Nanny. What about that room?

650
00:41:10,620 --> 00:41:12,000
Nothing there!

651
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:14,960
What happened? Where did he go?

652
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,320
How come...

653
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:21,840
Chang'er is missing.

654
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:24,800
Manniang and her brother

655
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:25,680
are both missing!

656
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:28,080
I want my mother!

657
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:42,920
What are you doing?

658
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:45,160
Sorry.
